### 2.4 GraphQL Resolver 개선 (커서 기반 페이지네이션)

**파일: `api/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/graphql/follow/FollowResolver.kt`**

```kotlin
// After - 커서 기반 페이지네이션 적용
@QueryMapping
fun followingList(
    @AuthenticationPrincipal userId: String,
    @Argument first: Int = 20,
    @Argument after: String? = null,  // 커서 (마지막 followId)
): FollowConnection {
    val pageable = PageRequest.of(0, first, Sort.by("createdAt").descending())
    val result = followService.getFollowingList(userId, pageable)

    return FollowConnection(
        edges = result.content.map { projection ->
            FollowEdge(
                cursor = projection.followId,
                node = FollowUserDto(
                    userId = projection.userId,
                    nickname = projection.nickname,
                    profileImageUrl = projection.profileImageUrl,
                )
            )
        },
        pageInfo = PageInfo(
            hasNextPage = result.hasNext(),
            endCursor = result.content.lastOrNull()?.followId,
        )
    )
}
```

**GraphQL 스키마:**

```graphql
type Query {
  followingList(first: Int = 20, after: String): FollowConnection!
}

type FollowConnection {
  edges: [FollowEdge!]!
  pageInfo: PageInfo!
}

type FollowEdge {
  cursor: String!
  node: FollowUser!
}

type FollowUser {
  userId: ID!
  nickname: String!
  profileImageUrl: String
}

type PageInfo {
  hasNextPage: Boolean!
  endCursor: String
}
```

---

### 2.5 개선된 Entity (인덱스 어노테이션 반영)

**파일: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/follow/FollowEntity.kt`**

```kotlin
// After - 인덱스 추가, 불필요한 연관관계 제거
@Entity
@Table(
    catalog = "maum",
    name = "follow",
    indexes = [
        Index(
            name = "idx_follow_follower_id_created_at",
            columnList = "follower_id, created_at DESC"
        ),
        Index(
            name = "idx_follow_followee_id_created_at",
            columnList = "followee_id, created_at DESC"
        ),
    ],
    uniqueConstraints = [
        UniqueConstraint(
            name = "uq_follow_follower_followee",
            columnNames = ["follower_id", "followee_id"]
        )
    ]
)
class FollowEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    @Column(name = "follower_id", nullable = false)
    val followerId: String,

    @Column(name = "followee_id", nullable = false)
    val followeeId: String,

    // 단방향 ID 참조만 유지 - @ManyToOne 연관관계 제거로 N+1 원천 차단
    // User 정보 필요시 QueryDSL JOIN으로 처리

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

